            <!-- Section 2: Poe Chatbot -->
            <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm group">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-xl text-gray-900">
                    2. Poe Chatbot for Text-Based Business Tasks
                    <span class="plus-icon text-blue-500 text-2xl transform transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 space-y-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">2.1 What is Poe?</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2">Poe (poe.com) is a platform where you can create a custom AI assistant by setting its instructions, personality, and example prompts.</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Best for:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
                            <li>Client Q&A</li>
                            <li>Proposal or report generation</li>
                            <li>Internal knowledge base</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">2.2 Step-by-Step Guide to Creating a Poe Business Bot</h3>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 space-y-3 pl-4">
                            <li><strong>Sign Up and Access Bot Builder:</strong> Go to poe.com, sign up, and click "Create a bot."</li>
                            <li><strong>Choose a Base Model:</strong> Select Claude for detailed explanations or GPT-4o for short, clear answers based on your needs.</li>
                            <li><strong>Write Bot Instructions:</strong> Clearly define the bot's role, audience, tone, and boundaries.</li>
                            <li><strong>Add a Welcome Message:</strong> Create a welcoming first message for users.</li>
                            <li><strong>Create Suggested Prompts:</strong> Provide clickable examples for users.</li>
                            <li><strong>Save and Test:</strong> Test with various queries to check tone, accuracy, and formatting.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Poe Self-Guided Practice</h3>
                        <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
                            <p class="font-semibold">Task: Create a Poe bot for a business of your choice.</p>
                            <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Write bot instructions (150–200 words).</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Add welcome message (1–2 sentences).</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Add 3 suggested prompts.</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Test and refine based on feedback.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                             <p class="font-semibold">Self-Check Questions:</p>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Does the bot answer in a way that matches your brand tone?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Does it know when to escalate to a human?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Are its answers consistent when asked similar questions?</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4 border-t pt-4">
                             <label class="flex items-center font-bold text-green-700"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-green-600 border-gray-400 rounded focus:ring-green-500 mr-3">Mark Poe Chatbot Activity as Completed</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
