            <!-- Section 3: Meta AI Studio -->
            <details class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm group">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer font-semibold text-xl text-gray-900">
                    3. Meta AI Studio for Social Media Engagement
                    <span class="plus-icon text-blue-500 text-2xl transform transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 space-y-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">3.1 What is Meta AI Studio?</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2">Meta AI Studio lets you create AI characters for Messenger, Instagram, and WhatsApp.</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Best for:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
                            <li>Marketing interactions</li>
                            <li>Customer service on social channels</li>
                            <li>Lead qualification</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">3.2 Step-by-Step Guide to Creating a Meta AI Business Bot</h3>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 space-y-3 pl-4">
                            <li><strong>Access AI Studio:</strong> Visit ai.meta.com, log in with your Meta business account, and click "Create AI."</li>
                            <li><strong>Name & Describe the Bot:</strong> Give your bot a clear name and description.</li>
                            <li><strong>Set Personality & Behavior:</strong> Define its style, do's, and don'ts.</li>
                            <li><strong>Add Welcome Message & Starters:</strong> Craft a greeting and provide example prompts.</li>
                            <li><strong>Enable Features:</strong> Enable search if needed and set public/private access.</li>
                            <li><strong>Publish & Test:</strong> Test for quick responses, clear options, and brand-safe language.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Meta AI Studio Self-Guided Practice</h3>
                        <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
                             <p class="font-semibold">Task: Build a social media bot for a business scenario.</p>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Define name, description, and personality.</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Add welcome message and 3 starter prompts.</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Test with a clear query, a vague request, and an off-topic question.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                             <p class="font-semibold">Self-Check Questions:</p>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Does it engage naturally and encourage conversation?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Does it avoid unsafe or off-brand responses?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500 mr-2">Is it easy for the user to continue chatting?</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4 border-t pt-4">
                             <label class="flex items-center font-bold text-green-700"><input type="checkbox" class="progress-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-green-600 border-gray-400 rounded focus:ring-green-500 mr-3">Mark Meta AI Studio Activity as Completed</label>
                        </div>
